import React from 'react';
import {Container ,Content,List,Line} from './style'
const FiliallarNomi = () => {
  return <Container>
         <Content>
              <List  style={{marginRight:'186px' ,marginLeft:'76px'}}>Filial nomi (UZ)</List>
                  <Line></Line>
              <List style={{marginRight:'103.5px'}}>Filial nomi (Ru)</List>
                  <Line></Line>
              <List style={{marginRight:'135px'}}>Mo’ljal</List>
                   <Line></Line>
              <List style={{marginRight:'187.5px'}}>Qo’shimcha</List>
                  <Line></Line>
              <List>ACTION</List>
         </Content>
  </Container>
};

export default FiliallarNomi;
